{"tid":1182484,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《認哥》下期嘉賓為樂童音樂家李燦赫&李秀賢、SOMI！","createTime":"2019-06-02T08:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T08:42:26.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db18e2114dc9b67eed99b698a724a644c54aa80f","tid":1182484,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_faf747f92212c173981106e26f316dbb/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117186-740201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_faf747f92212c173981106e26f316dbb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117186-740201.jpg&h=81aeb950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《認哥》下期嘉賓為樂童音樂家李燦赫&amp;李秀賢、SOMI！剛從「海軍陸戰隊」退伍的李燦赫，公開在軍隊裡遇到「歌壇前輩」SHINee珉豪的軼事。不禁拍掌大笑：「原來網友們說的是真的！XD」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e953174ce8a02b294c288c6a6e77baea/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117186-740207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e953174ce8a02b294c288c6a6e77baea%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117186-740207.jpg&h=d3231bf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂童音樂家李燦赫&amp;李秀賢、SOMI一同作為嘉賓，將出演下週六（8日）播出的JTBC綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》。<br />\n<br />\n李燦赫從「海軍陸戰隊」退伍後的第二天，便參與《認哥》的錄製，所以還很有軍人的感覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_99f3c94d8b27cf6f65fc88546d950157/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117186-740213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_99f3c94d8b27cf6f65fc88546d950157%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117186-740213.jpg&h=e0287984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a05fee9fc2bdf30c5066f921ed743f04/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117186-740220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a05fee9fc2bdf30c5066f921ed743f04%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117186-740220.jpg&h=af3630d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_715435bce7030d834877f05ebf012cae/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117186-740223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_715435bce7030d834877f05ebf012cae%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117186-740223.jpg&h=784110b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即將SOLO出道的SOMI，向哥哥們表示：「請夏姐姐和世正姐姐說要幫我&hellip;」就在哥哥們引頸期盼、兩位女歌手出現在現場時，SOMI自己帶來姐姐的舞蹈COVER！藝能感滿滿～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fgIGG12jQ6I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfgIGG12jQ6I&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=6478d560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fgIGG12jQ6I</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c1195cac1320ff22f42680ef621adf8e1d71c2","tid":1182484,"uid":124156,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"認唔出somi <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6aead21046fec155d705c9c11d98edc7af7b57","tid":1182484,"uid":142021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"樂童<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f202a3f700b989af5e5c316e4b1b29da7de67571","tid":1182484,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76c1195cac1320ff22f42680ef621adf8e1d71c2","tid":1182484,"uid":124156,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"認唔出somi <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk